long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
SupplyPike browser extension delivers shipping documents to you when and where you need them, in retailer dispute portals.

The best way to experience SupplyPike’s automated proof documentation retrieval, organization, and delivery is in the browser. Easily retrieve or request proofs of delivery or bills of lading relevant to a retailer or carrier claim while you’re in the portal creating the dispute.

This extension requires a SupplyPike subscription. If you don’t have one yet, you can click the link to get started with a Free Trial. https://app.supplypike.com/sign-up

SupplyPike is a software automation company helping suppliers recover retailer deductions quickly and easily. SupplyPike’s Deductions Navigator fully automates the dispute process with 1 click disputing, increasing recovery rate, and helping stop deductions before they happen at Walmart, Kroger, and Target. The browser extension automates the most timely piece of disputing with other retailers: hunting down, organizing, storing, and providing proof documentation needed for successful disputes.
